metadata.description:
We are as big as the Universe
not because the universe is as small as a human being
but becuse a human being can Conceive the entirety of the universe.

We are more than animals,
stronger than chaos,
we are not just randomness,
we are the the best shape,
among billions of possible shapes,
for LOGOS, to manifest itself.
